    {"type":"text","id":"zbHdr","x":1115,"y":120,"width":700,"height":24,"text":"B · Two modes — split on failed","originalText":"B · Two modes — split on failed","fontSize":20,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#1e40af","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":820002,"version":1,"versionNonce":820003,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":null,"lineHeight":1.25},

    {"type":"rectangle","id":"zbSt","x":1115,"y":166,"width":485,"height":164,"strokeColor":"#1e40af","backgroundColor":"#dbeafe","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":820010,"version":1,"versionNonce":820011,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":[{"id":"zbStt","type":"text"}],"link":null,"locked":false,"roundness":{"type":3}},
    {"type":"text","id":"zbStt","x":1131,"y":180,"width":455,"height":136,"text":"STATIC  ·  failed == false\n\nRead-only — resolved via staticCallLookup →\n_resolveStaticLookup. Sub-calls run as STATICCALL,\nhashed with the UNTAGGED schema.\nNo nested table: callCount == 0,\nexpectedL1ToL2Calls empty.","originalText":"STATIC  ·  failed == false\n\nRead-only — resolved via staticCallLookup →\n_resolveStaticLookup. Sub-calls run as STATICCALL,\nhashed with the UNTAGGED schema.\nNo nested table: callCount == 0,\nexpectedL1ToL2Calls empty.","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#1e40af","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":820012,"version":1,"versionNonce":820013,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":null,"lineHeight":1.4},

    {"type":"rectangle","id":"zbFa","x":1620,"y":166,"width":485,"height":164,"strokeColor":"#b91c1c","backgroundColor":"#fee2e2","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":820020,"version":1,"versionNonce":820021,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":[{"id":"zbFat","type":"text"}],"link":null,"locked":false,"roundness":{"type":3}},
    {"type":"text","id":"zbFat","x":1636,"y":180,"width":455,"height":136,"text":"FAILED  ·  failed == true\n\nRuns as a mini-entry (_executeRevertedLookup):\nreal calls, TAGGED schema, reentry from its own\ntable, deeper lookups from the active host —\nthen reverts with returnData (the terminal revert\nrolls the sub-execution's state back).","originalText":"FAILED  ·  failed == true\n\nRuns as a mini-entry (_executeRevertedLookup):\nreal calls, TAGGED schema, reentry from its own\ntable, deeper lookups from the active host —\nthen reverts with returnData (the terminal revert\nrolls the sub-execution's state back).","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#b91c1c","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":820022,"version":1,"versionNonce":820023,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":null,"lineHeight":1.4},

    {"type":"rectangle","id":"zbPart","x":1115,"y":350,"width":990,"height":160,"strokeColor":"#13263d","backgroundColor":"#1e3a5f","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":820030,"version":1,"versionNonce":820031,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":[{"id":"zbPartt","type":"text"}],"link":null,"locked":false,"roundness":{"type":3}},
    {"type":"text","id":"zbPartt","x":1131,"y":364,"width":960,"height":132,"text":"callCount partition (reverted real sub-execution only):\n   callCount + Σ expectedL1ToL2Calls[i].callCount  ==  l2ToL1Calls.length\n\n   failed == false   ⇒   callCount == 0, no nested table          (static)\n   callCount  > 0    ⇒   failed == true, real sub-execution, tagged hash\n   l2ToL1Calls.length > 0  with  callCount == 0   →   INVALID  (UnconsumedL2ToL1Calls)","originalText":"callCount partition (reverted real sub-execution only):\n   callCount + Σ expectedL1ToL2Calls[i].callCount  ==  l2ToL1Calls.length\n\n   failed == false   ⇒   callCount == 0, no nested table          (static)\n   callCount  > 0    ⇒   failed == true, real sub-execution, tagged hash\n   l2ToL1Calls.length > 0  with  callCount == 0   →   INVALID  (UnconsumedL2ToL1Calls)","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#bfdbfe","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":820032,"version":1,"versionNonce":820033,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":null,"lineHeight":1.5},

